From 38970a9215e752f3d95e758c63694d88729fc252 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Apr 2026 22:35:46 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] android-headers: bump ANDROID_VERSION_MAJOR to 12 for Halium
 12 targets

The Volla X23 (MT6789) runs Android 12 (SDK 32). Update the version header
so libhybris and the HWC2/Gralloc VDI wrappers see the correct Android ABI
when compiling against these headers.

Part of Phase 5 (libhybris integration & HAL bridge) for hybris_generic.
---
 android-version.h | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/android-version.h b/android-version.h
index 9c6b6fb..e6abd00 100644
--- a/android-version.h
+++ b/android-version.h
@@ -1,7 +1,7 @@
 #ifndef ANDROID_VERSION_H_
 #define ANDROID_VERSION_H_
 
-#define ANDROID_VERSION_MAJOR 11
+#define ANDROID_VERSION_MAJOR 12
 #define ANDROID_VERSION_MINOR 0
 #define ANDROID_VERSION_PATCH 0
 #define ANDROID_VERSION_PATCH2 0
-- 
2.50.1

